{"id":"b9e737a761bc368ada8da2c74652f4fec276df3430e8d0d924372658dac841a7","item_id":"39daab3c51:0","text":"Artists（艺术家）可以使用 RenderMan 的 Preset Browser，在不同 DCCs 和部门之间保存并共享 materials（材质）、dome lights（穹顶灯）和 light rigs（灯光装置）。"}
{"id":"c0e45c02d94b23272c5510c5f6e3a31b37b181eab1cac04bd85f9eff49e99712","item_id":"39daab3c51:1","text":"Preset Browser 可在 Solaris context（Solaris 上下文）中使用，并可在 RenderMan → Preset Browser 下找到。"}
{"id":"a7a9db3d28e5d7f8e552256af20234947f7c64344e3223b1af266c33ad8aff2d","item_id":"39daab3c51:2","text":"Loading HDRIs（加载 HDRI）"}
{"id":"db2e21f771612a50e4163bcc2829a114be9e915cb2ef33a17af16b36884ef180","item_id":"39daab3c51:3","text":"Environment maps（环境贴图）可以很容易加载到现有 domelight 节点中：先选择要附加贴图的 domelight 节点，然后选择"}
{"id":"afb1166232e70867d9fd47c0a2e7eff675c01a94b17d518474ec3b504d3a0a4e","item_id":"39daab3c51:4","text":"Import and Assign to Selected（导入并分配给选中项）"}
{"id":"79872ef12628d294592ca3ae008fd867b66cc3d54ba9fc420f612d7309dd5b6d","item_id":"39daab3c51:5","text":"如果没有选择 domelight 节点时选择 Import，会自动创建一个 domelight 节点，并分配选中的 environment map（环境贴图）。"}
{"id":"f8bf61fb6a534ed5f89048e3975992dd4ccfedd1fee6a90b48c49edb7c5f4ddd","item_id":"39daab3c51:6","text":"Loading Materials（加载材质）"}
{"id":"eed821e5cc53ebd95640bb1a4c306fb28480c3d88a78b417ab438c2795c07c64","item_id":"39daab3c51:7","text":"如果已有一个 Solaris Material Library 节点，并希望把 preset material（预设材质）加载进去，只需选择"}
{"id":"cd6b542886cebcd3bc6d6586d2130be8e85426bd46c3b020bede0a23452c81cb","item_id":"39daab3c51:8","text":"materiallibrary"}
{"id":"82e28640c82b623f9a4e9008b69f463b6e18ad8ebf7eed65f284ecbaa02df8d3","item_id":"39daab3c51:9","text":"节点，然后选择 Import into Selected Material Library。"}
{"id":"4bc230f8bc07e8435aec3d710d23b1b85b336f09f58788acb42e27f89b5938a0","item_id":"39daab3c51:10","text":"这会将选中的 material preset（材质预设）导入到选中的 Material Library 中。"}
{"id":"b8a73ac8d01b66dccbf3cd8815dcc737cdd9fcdd0951370ce187488eff11ee9c","item_id":"39daab3c51:11","text":"如果"}
{"id":"cd6b542886cebcd3bc6d6586d2130be8e85426bd46c3b020bede0a23452c81cb","item_id":"39daab3c51:12","text":"materiallibrary"}
{"id":"ecf9a533b700ef0e1f09611642db833372d8c43eb8f4460c66657ca4d11adde2","item_id":"39daab3c51:13","text":"节点未被选择或不存在，可以选择 Import 或 Import and Assign to Selected，该 preset 会被加载到新创建的 Material Library 中。"}
{"id":"95c02552fe353100b50e1e091404696334d15c94fd2f8461ddc571b9b76cff0d","item_id":"39daab3c51:14","text":"Saving Materials（保存材质）"}
{"id":"32876da39153f2706cffbc38fcdaa8d24da918971739a6adca1b925843cd05f8","item_id":"39daab3c51:15","text":"目前 Solaris 中有一个限制：从选中的"}
{"id":"cd6b542886cebcd3bc6d6586d2130be8e85426bd46c3b020bede0a23452c81cb","item_id":"39daab3c51:16","text":"materiallibrary"}
{"id":"cdb4ee2aea69cc6a83331bbe96dc2caa9a299d21329efb0336fc02a82e1839a8","item_id":"39daab3c51:17","text":"中只会导出一个材质。"}
{"id":"672505bcd65064df26160576b21227426b55c05a4b812a5d37c5db07d14e02e7","item_id":"39daab3c51:18","text":"只需选择"}
{"id":"cd6b542886cebcd3bc6d6586d2130be8e85426bd46c3b020bede0a23452c81cb","item_id":"39daab3c51:19","text":"materiallibrary"}
{"id":"b01ea8ab86c90c8c31ddd2c473ddaa13b8044ddaabd269502c5df837f10b3aea","item_id":"39daab3c51:20","text":"节点，然后点击 Preset Browser 中的新建材质图标。"}
